data.description: Beautiful custom built home perfectly situated in a sought after community. As you walk up, you get a sense of home. Your den/office is just off the entry way next to the master bedroom, a private door leads to the back. Main living area you can appreciate the open style floor plan w/ towering ceilings, fans, double sided FP, top of the line mill work, and the Kitchen is something out of a magazine. Granite counters tops and high quality custom cabinets.  Just off the kitchen is a door leading to Pacific Northwest ultimate outdoor entertainment for friends & guests all year long. Keep warm outside next to the double sided FP and take in the majestic views of Mount Rainier or entertain guests at the covered cabana w/ FP, speaker system, and wired for a sauna/spa. This home was well thought out and one of a kind.
data.whatILove: When I walk in the first thing that I can appreciate is the den and master bedroom are at one end of the house away from the kitchen and living area which creates a quiet atmosphere and then there is the Kitchen, It's huge long island has room for plenty of people to sit around and talk with.  And who doesn't hang out in the kitchen?  What is really something else is the details that went into the mill work, under counter lighting, cabinet lighting and the the window bay faces the back out towards the pool.  The outdoor entertainment is something anyone could appreciate all year long.  Stamped concrete everywhere! In the summer time you can slide down the slide into the pool including a waterfall. Mountain views are incredible.  In the summer and winter times you can be covered under the cabana either lounging around & BBQ or in winter time be next to the fire.  Another double sided Fireplace is under the covered patio area just off the door to the kitchen.  From the back yard you can't see the detached 3 car garage with private apartment perfect for the MIL or college student wanting there own privacy.  Travel times from property to highway your looking at a max 5 minutes and to SR512 (15 minutes).  This is a property located within a sought after neighborhood with higher end properties, your investment is solid.
